This skill uses the Key Phrase machine learning models provided byAzure AI Language. This capability is useful if you need to quickly identify the main talking points in therecord. For example, given input text "The food was delicious and there were wonderfulstaff", the service returns "food" and "wonderful staff".Microsoft.Skills.Text.KeyPhraseExtractionSkillThe maximum size of a record should be 50,000 characters as measured byString.Length.
